{
  "stem": "1473.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rose and Louis Clot, C-L-O-T.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told me one morning, you know, we got to go there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have news about your parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we took the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember it was a big office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the man had a big desk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he took a bunch of paper in front of you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he explained it to me, just like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[SNAPS] He explained Auschwitz to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SNAPS] Except I didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, I have papers here to show that your parents were deported on a convoy-- and he gave me the date-- from [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dronsea ?] to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I also have evidence that they never spent a day in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they either died on the way or were immediately gassed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what that meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, well, if they didn't get there, so they got off somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember him saying, and him saying, no, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Those were sealed cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was just as I'm speaking to you now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it didn't pene-- it didn't penetrate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One thing penetrated, that he said my parents were-- were dead, and he was wrong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The fact of Auschwitz, the fact of cattle-- all of this just washed by me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, if I'm very careful, if I go to work here, I'm going to find my parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember on the way back they were so sad, [FRENCH] Louis and [FRENCH] Rose.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were so sad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember the conversation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We will adopt you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You will stay with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it sounded so absurd to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They will adopt me and I'll be with them?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was all alien.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
